		"content": {
			"start": 7,
			"end": 242,
			"styles": "\n\t/* leading + on a coefficient: tsv keeps it glued to the An+B term */\n\t:foo(+2n + 1) {\n\t\tcolor: red;\n\t}\n\n\t/* leading + on a plain integer B */\n\t:is(+3) {\n\t\tcolor: blue;\n\t}\n\n\t/* leading + on a bare n */\n\t:not(+n) {\n\t\tcolor: green;\n\t}\n",
